nmap <C-n>c :NERDTreeClose<CR>
nmap <C-n>n :NERDTree<CR>
nmap <C-n>t :NERDTreeToggle<CR>
nmap <C-n>fi :NERDTreeFind<CR>

" EasyMotion
set easymotion






